      "text": [
        "2167 - وَ رُوِيَ : «أَنَّ اَلْحَاجَّ إِذَا سَعَى بَيْنَ اَلصَّفَا وَ اَلْمَرْوَةِ خَرَجَ مِنْ ذُنُوبِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2167 - It has been narrated: \"When the pilgrim performs Sa’y between Safa and Marwah, they are cleansed of their sins.\""
        ]
      }
